1074 - Extended Traffic

Problem link : http://lightoj.com/volume_showproblem.php?problem=1074

you know how busy each junction is...
store it in an array or a vector

you have to visualize the problem diffently...

source and destination of an is given
weight of the edge (busyness of destination - busyness of source)^3

then simply run a bellman ford.

